Amplify,is,a,web,service,developed,by,Hapax,that,brings,human,understanding,to,content,Using,patented,Natural,Language,Processing,technology,Amplify,reads,and,understands,every,word,used,in,text,It,identifies,the,significant,topics,brands,people,perspectives,emotions,actions,and,timescales,and,presents,the,findings,in,an,actionable,XML,structure